# rateLimited

**Type Property**

An error code that indicates your app requested its status too frequently.

## Declaration

```swift
static var rateLimited: UIApplication.CategoryDefaultError.Code { get }
```

## Errors when discovering if an app is the default in a category

- **errorDomain**: A string that indicates that an error happened when the system attempted to determine if your app is the default in a category.
